name: Fishlabs
description: Mobile games for avid gamers on the go!
overview:
Spearheading the mobile games industry since 2004, Fishlabs Entertainment is one of the world’s leading independent developers and publishers of international top titles for feature phones, smartphones and tablets.

With an award-winning portfolio of critically acclaimed core titles such as Galaxy on Fire™, DEEP™, Blades & Magic™, Rally Master Pro™ and Snowboard Hero™ under its belt, the Hamburg-based studio has launched an impressive selection of high-end 3D action, racing, sports and RPG games on a huge variety of platforms, including Java, BREW, Symbian^3, iOS, Android, BlackBerry OS and Mac OS. All of Fishlabs’ titles have been developed with the company’s platform independent in-house technology ABYSS®.

Fishlabs Entertainment’s flagship title Galaxy on Fire 2™ has not only been featured globally by Apple several times but it has also been pre-installed on several devices or promoted by Nokia, Sony Mobile, Samsung, Lenovo and Nvidia. So far, the Galaxy on Fire 2™ series has spawned one main game and two extensive story add-ons by the names of Valkyrie™ and Supernova™.

In addition to its own IPs, Fishlabs Entertainment is also known as world leader for the development of numerous highly successful brand games for blue-chip clients such as Volkswagen and Barclaycard, which have dominated the App Store download charts in a multitude of countries for weeks. All in all, the company’s titles have generated a total of more than 100 million game installs.

For more information visit www.fishlabs.net.
